264
00:20:12,953 --> 00:20:14,969
appelé "white lodge"

265
00:20:14,899 --> 00:20:16,453
c'est confidentiel

266
00:20:16,966 --> 00:20:18,915
Colonnel, nous voudrions vous aider

267
00:20:18,972 --> 00:20:21,156
mais il faut nous en dire d'avantage

268
00:20:22,670 --> 00:20:24,380
Garland Briggs

269
00:20:24,964 --> 00:20:27,408
