411
00:30:17,310 --> 00:30:19,374
affaires internes du FBl.

412
00:30:19,459 --> 00:30:21,193
Je croyais que vous étiez suspendu ?

413
00:30:21,259 --> 00:30:22,668
je le suis

414
00:30:22,737 --> 00:30:24,075
merci encore

415
00:30:24,347 --> 00:30:25,359
bonsoir.

416
00:30:27,821 --> 00:30:31,324
