453
00:32:49,279 --> 00:32:50,868
Oui?

454
00:32:50,950 --> 00:32:52,875
Comment je peux dire...

455
00:32:52,935 --> 00:32:55,259
Voilà, en fait,

456
00:32:55,381 --> 00:32:58,083
J'ai tendance à penser

457
00:32:58,191 --> 00:33:01,185
